Interface Occupant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Combatant
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Occupant
extends Entity
    An occupant is an extension of an entity that is able to occupy a tile on the grid.
    Author:
    Matt Imel
